By: Sri Ramakrishna
---
The sunlight is one and the same wherever it falls, but only bright surfaces
like water, mirrors and polished metals can reflect it fully. So is the divine
light. It falls equally and impartially on all hearts, but only the pure and
clean hearts of the good and holy can fully reflect it.
